Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.03,0:00:07.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你已經到這裏幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:11.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也該明白這社殿的狀況了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:15.77,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這裏只有衣服看上去華貴而已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:18.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}其實和坐牢沒什麼區別
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:21.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說到翼人  是神的使者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.64,0:00:23.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當遇到饑荒和疫病時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:25.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}祈禱神的力量來保護大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是可以直接和神對話的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}本以為會生活的更舒服些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:35.45,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有翅膀也不一定就是神的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的翅膀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.58,0:00:38.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}收起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:41.26,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}平時看起來和一般人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.52,0:00:44.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:46.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼  看上去形狀滿好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.95,0:00:49.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你只要看到形狀好的就要一個一個上去摸摸看嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:51.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒用的東西！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:54.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉  你笑什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:58.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在笑神奈大人害羞的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這些都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:03.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不要總是隱匿氣息地接近我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.51,0:01:05.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今天柳也大人也被召見了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.96,0:01:09.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來神奈大人真的很喜歡您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.57,0:01:11.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}絕無此事～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.57,0:01:16.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是在教這沒用無禮的蠢材呆瓜應有的禮儀！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:21.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如此得到神奈大人賞目的  您還是第一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.05,0:03:02.55,AIR Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,770)}夏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:05.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人  給您這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.02,0:03:10.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我剛才在酒殿後面的地窖裏找到了這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.32,0:03:15.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都已經是盛夏了  沒想到還能有冰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想必須稟告您  所以就拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦  那真是很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:26.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個地窖是冰室  隨便進入可是重罪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.36,0:03:27.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哎呀哎呀  真是的真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好危險  好危險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.53,0:03:31.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…果然是你倆串通好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:35.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:38.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也你可以嘗嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:43.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}吃神奈大人的供品可也是重罪的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.59,0:03:45.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你自己還不是在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:53.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣三個人坐在一起吃冰的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就像寒冬中無衣無食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:59.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}坐在屋檐下的積雪上忍凍挨餓的  瀕死的落魄一家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:02.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的是非常有趣的比喻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:05.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}家族是什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:09.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  非要說的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.66,0:04:13.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂！ 大熱天的不要靠得這麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.64,0:04:17.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}等等  也不用那麼害怕  過來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:19.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不是說了不要貼那麼緊的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}也不用離我那麼遠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:25.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼你也過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:26.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒什麼  情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:28.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}兩個人都從我身邊離開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.98,0:04:31.56,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們在耍我嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:36.34,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所謂家族  就是大家聚在一起生活
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:40.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈是從什麼時候開始過著這樣的生活的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:43.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自從柳也大人您赴任以來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人就變得如此開朗了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:46.51,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不是指這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.02,0:04:49.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是問她從什麼時候開始生活在這個社殿中的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.26,0:04:54.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為我來到這裏還不到半年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.48,0:04:59.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過神奈大人說過  在她懂事時就已經被這樣關著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:01.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有談話的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}生活在奔走各個社殿的生活中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.83,0:05:13.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:15.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到了換班的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:22.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在緊張什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.20,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}自從來到這裏後就一直提心吊膽的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.74,0:05:31.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}接近神奈備命大人的話  會受到神罰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:34.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}據我看好像不會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.04,0:05:38.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我聽說翼人是不祥與邪惡的化身
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.35,0:05:40.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想趕快恢復普通的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.58,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:52.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也你做夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}有時做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:57.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}怎麼  做了惡夢後睡不著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.38,0:05:59.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢到了從前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.43,0:06:04.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}幼小的我坐在像現在這樣的黑暗中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:07.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}什麼也看不見
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}連自己是否存在都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.84,0:06:12.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}又是害怕又是寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.64,0:06:14.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但即使如此也不能哭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:16.28,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣的一段日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.75,0:06:20.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在夢中看到過一團溫暖的光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:22.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是一個人影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.49,0:06:25.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但當我想追上去時就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:29.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不止一次  總是重複著這樣的夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:33.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也知道那人影是誰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:36.43,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是你的母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.61,0:06:40.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不記得自己的母親了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:44.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢是曾經見過的景象的回放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.84,0:06:47.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以就算你不記得了但卻見過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.11,0:06:51.91,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我的身體記住了母親的溫暖麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果是的話  那就不是一個惡夢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.64,0:07:05.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好想見母親
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:09.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有比見不到母親更殘酷的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:15.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「神奈備命須祈禱五穀豐登」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.57,0:07:18.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}「將遷往北面社殿居住」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.42,0:07:21.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}出發定在立秋前的大暑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.32,0:07:29.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們也跟隨神奈備命一起去新的社殿嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.95,0:07:31.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  我們全部留下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}進行土地開墾的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我已經聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.16,0:07:43.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}每年這個時候都有同樣的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我今天早上才知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:49.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到時候就和你還有裏葉分別了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}已經沒幾天了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.09,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:56.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}願意什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.52,0:07:59.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我在問你真的願意和我還有裏葉分開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}新的住處也會有怪人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:04.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但我和裏葉不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.45,0:08:05.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別臭美了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.68,0:08:08.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我看起來有那麼沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就算沒有你  我也可以活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.66,0:08:17.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到目前為止我可都是這樣活過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.86,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不是很寂寞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不是想要見到母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:27.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想見見不到也是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.89,0:08:32.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的母親死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.56,0:08:33.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.06,0:08:36.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有死…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:40.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親一定在什麼地方守護著我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.20,0:08:52.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉  神奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.11,0:08:53.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我現在很忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:57.73,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:09:00.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如您所見  我在做旅行的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:03.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}離開的只有神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.19,0:09:04.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們都將留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.03,0:09:08.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以才要在那之前先走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:10.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}終日過著這樣的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人真是太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.89,0:09:16.85,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}可以問一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.04,0:09:19.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你為什麼那麼在意神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:25.92,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也正想問柳也大人同樣的問題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:29.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是啊  非要說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:32.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒有人比她更值得耍著玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:34.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}的確是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:39.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.12,0:09:40.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.44,0:09:43.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}早上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊！  有可疑人物！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別鬧  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你不想見你母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:56.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我受命保護你  絕對不可以違背神奈備命的旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.95,0:10:01.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}所以只要你說想見母親  我就為你赴湯蹈火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.92,0:10:06.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是否賜予我作為主人的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你真的願意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一切由你決定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那麼  我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.53,0:10:25.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}將我帶到母親的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}正八位下左衛門大志  柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:34.94,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}發誓不違背神奈備命之命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:42.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:43.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}快走
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:46.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也大人  請稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.04,0:10:49.74,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為似乎還沒有被人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:51.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}早晚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不久就會大騷亂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:54.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然都這時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.07,0:10:57.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過想想  我們真的做了很大膽的行動呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:10:59.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都到這地步了  不要再發牢騷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:02.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:08.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}社殿到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:10.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:13.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過看樣子最好立刻離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.75,0:11:21.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.27,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}看來是被包圍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.69,0:11:25.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈  裏葉  準備全力向前衝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.22,0:11:28.80,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}衝！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}把刀扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:46.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}老實回答我的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:49.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們是關東來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.55,0:11:51.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼要抓神奈備命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.42,0:11:52.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:54.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}上邊是這樣的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們想把神奈備命怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:58.01,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是誰讓你們這樣做的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:58.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.07,0:12:01.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}上頭這樣吩咐的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.79,0:12:02.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:07.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:17.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你想傷害他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.60,0:12:20.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不那樣做的話  我們的生命就會受到威脅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:22.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}羞不羞！  你這個傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:27.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你將人命當兒戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.01,0:12:28.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.75,0:12:31.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我不想要這樣的人保護！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.32,0:12:37.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要你還當我是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.24,0:12:40.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今後就不許再殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:41.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}記住
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:47.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}緊記在心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.84,0:12:52.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過  你真以為不殺一人就能平安離去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:56.70,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想對於柳也大人是很容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:58.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別說的這麼輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:07.89,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}到底是從什麼地方找到這樣的衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.14,0:13:11.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是從河邊晾曬的衣服中取來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.71,0:13:14.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}當然  我把錢留下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.67,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}挺合適你的  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.83,0:13:18.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:20.54,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真是奇怪的愛好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:22.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人很奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:24.25,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}換衣服時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.36,0:13:28.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}說是無法在柳也面前穿這種見不得人的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我沒有那麼說！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不怎麼好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:49.90,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣三個人坐在一起吃乾糧的樣子  簡直…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.96,0:13:51.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就像是被調往偏僻地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:55.31,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不甘心地吃著沾滿眼淚的乾糧的  某處的大官一家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:58.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的是非常風雅的比喻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是手包
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}裏葉說是原本放在衣服裏的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不過用布做的手包很少見呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}一般是往裏填石子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:15.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣做應該是母親怕孩子玩時受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我也可以作到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:20.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想學習一下就一定會變得擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:26.24,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:31.60,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}萬事開頭難
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:33.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}重要的在於不懈努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:36.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}剛才只是失手了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:37.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}嘿！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.89,0:14:40.76,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不可以過分用力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:42.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}要拋到大概齊眉的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:43.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:44.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:48.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}…沒想到會笨到這種地步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:51.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈大人您真是太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別說的那麼誇張！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.57,0:15:00.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.32,0:15:07.18,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我聽到消息  神奈大人的母親被關在紀州的靈山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}紀州是個什麼樣的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}離這裏很遠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.33,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}何況還要翻山越嶺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.74,0:15:15.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為了不讓追兵發現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:18.30,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們謹慎小心的前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:18.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}給
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.42,0:15:21.88,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.01,0:15:24.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:44.57,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}都過了一個月了  一點都沒長進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}偶爾也成功過的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.09,0:15:48.96,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}三天前我連續接住了三次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.35,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}哦？  那可真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你在拿我當傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:58.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這樣三個人在山邊圍火取暖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:01.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就像是拐了公主逃跑時美滋滋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}但卻對世道一無所知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:07.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}後悔當初不該如此的某處的大色狼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.54,0:16:10.50,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}真的是非常風趣的比喻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:13.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}與其說比喻  不如說就是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}紀州就在眼前了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:20.05,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像這樣的日子也沒有幾天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.15,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼大家看上去那麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:40.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像那樣歡聲起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}世間的煩惱就會消除了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:44.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.96,0:16:47.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}因為大家都相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.46,0:16:50.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}願望一定可以傳達到天上的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}誰來把願望帶去天上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:54.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:58.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我雖然有翅膀  但無法飛上天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.52,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}從小到大試了無數次了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.31,0:17:05.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別說飛上天了  想像樹葉那樣飄都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:07.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒用的一對翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.44,0:17:11.81,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}即使如此  只要祈禱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:14.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}願望就能傳達到天上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.92,0:17:18.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}會的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.44,0:17:24.06,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要心裏想著願望就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.58,0:17:26.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你的願望一定可以實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:28.69,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是吧  裏葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.21,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂  裏葉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.30,0:17:35.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很癢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:37.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.35,0:17:54.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}靜得讓人不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不可大意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我們應該已經進入靈山地界了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:05.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}好像布有結界  大家安靜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.84,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我覺得走這邊好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.98,0:18:09.68,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你知道路？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  是感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:24.82,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.76,0:18:30.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}武者法師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.52,0:18:32.32,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這裏不允許女人進入
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:36.16,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你這個鄉下武人來靈山幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不安的一個人走著夜路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.27,0:18:41.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}像是被野狐給耍了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.04,0:18:43.95,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  應該是野山貍才對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.38,0:18:47.00,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不能放過你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:51.03,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}讓你走出結界的話我們就無法動手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:04.53,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也小心背後！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:09.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}今後不允許你再殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:13.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊──！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.61,0:19:20.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:21.08,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}別過來！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.69,0:19:26.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:30.37,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不會讓你去見八百比丘尼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.44,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}八百…比丘尼…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.29,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}您醒過來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:48.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}太好了  好像熬過危險期了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.02,0:19:51.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我…  睡了多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:53.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}整整一天了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:56.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請您安心  我們已經穿過結界了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:58.61,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那些法師已經無法追來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.02,0:19:59.75,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:02.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我去打水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.77,0:20:06.83,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.19,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}沒受傷吧  神奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:15.87,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我…  曾經讓柳也不許殺傷別人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.85,0:20:17.93,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}現在想想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.99,0:20:21.07,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.76,0:20:23.63,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我可是忠臣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:26.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只要是神奈的命令一律服從
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.39,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}比如  如果你命令我不許死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:32.11,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我就絕對不會死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:38.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那…  我就命令你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.71,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}不  這不是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.33,0:20:43.65,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.98,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}柳也  不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.94,0:20:49.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}啊  一言為定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:53.62,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}這裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.83,0:20:54.41,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:56.40,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我能感覺到一些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:20:58.36,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親在這裏嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.85,0:20:59.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}很可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:01.23,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們閃開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:08.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請站住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:12.59,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果你們想鼓動我去參加戰爭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.71,0:21:14.99,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}就別想活著離開這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.86,0:21:19.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我是神奈備命的護衛柳也
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:24.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我想您就是神奈備命的母親吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:25.97,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈…？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.92,0:21:29.12,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}是… 母親嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.49,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.69,0:21:49.17,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}雖然不能拍打也不能飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.94,0:21:53.22,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}如果  您也有和我一樣的翅膀的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:55.66,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.58,0:21:57.64,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:01.42,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}那個叫柳也的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:06.47,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}請現在立刻帶著神奈下山去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.51,0:23:43.10,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}你們想要我如何
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:45.14,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}想請您離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:49.46,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}然後請您和神奈大人永遠幸福的生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:53.13,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.55,0:23:57.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}在某處安寧的土地上建一座小小的庵堂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:01.04,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}夢也不全是痛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:03.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}我很快樂…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.77,0:24:04.48,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}神奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:05.78,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.91,0:24:07.02,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}為什麼大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.73,0:24:09.55,AIR context 1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}{\blur4}只留下我一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.10,0:24:09.85,AIR Title2-2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,1080)}{\fad(1000,0)}月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.89,0:01:36.78,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}消失的航跡雲 我們目送遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.58,0:01:40.49,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因眩目而逃開
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.29,0:01:50.54,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}因懊悔而放手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:57.88,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}尚未抵達之地仍在遠方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:02:04.84,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}只有將願望深藏心中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.64,0:02:13.19,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}孩子們走在夏日的鐵軌上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.99,0:02:19.86,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,640)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}手中是將振翅高飛的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.95,0:02:27.87,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}消失的航跡雲 我們追了又追
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.57,0:02:36.92,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}從越過這山丘的那天起 就不曾改變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.72,0:02:43.59,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}總是執著不斷前進著的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.39,0:02:57.60,AIR OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,1000)\pos(960,1064)}{\blur6}一定能堅守像海神般的堅強
